{"tid":1199162,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"6月11號晚 我會企出來","createTime":"2019-06-10T12:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T12:25:38.000Z","uid":100860,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"421a6fe9b00d8df5862b72be7a767f60ebd80ca3","tid":1199162,"uid":100860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:02:17.000Z","msg":"先利申6月9我冇出到, 但6月11晚我會出來<br />\n<br />\n先為大家送上一段個人認為係呢幾年睇過最心酸的片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DhUFpd-qphA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDhUFpd-qphA&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=33c900e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DhUFpd-qphA</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完大家有d可能會有同感,會好驚,有d人可能會話會唔會太誇張<br />\n但我想講係冇, 呢個就係通過左之後一定會發生的事<br />\n唔信?<br />\n你可以望下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k4xkQDpliwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk4xkQDpliwU&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=dde03537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k4xkQDpliwU</a><br />\n之後又講左d咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=afnRQKJO3Fk&amp;t=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DafnRQKJO3Fk%26t%3D&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=d612b9f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=afnRQKJO3Fk&amp;t=</a><br />\n<br />\n各位仲想信冇做過怕咩姐的人醒下啦, 依家未過條例就已經有咁大個例子係度,<br />\n過左之後會有幾多人因為d咩懷疑偷睇國家機密文件而一車車人咁送番去<br />\n我已經唔夠膽再去想像.<br />\n<br />\n所以大家6月11唔該大家出來, 守護呢一個你住過的地方<br />\n(已經叫左2個fd一起出,準備叫埋d同事出)"},{"pid":"b2ab789f5171e89d9cbe02df4f92a5b08011c5c1","tid":1199162,"uid":52683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"如果你雨革坐係電視前面睇，魚革又係得個睇，琴日再睇多次，聽晚最後一戰 唔好再睇喇 企出黎啦"},{"pid":"708cf7031c2c97387a59ed7718c45f80b0225e75","tid":1199162,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"cite